name: Santiment Flags BTC and XRP in ‘Good Buy Zone’ Despite Sell‑Off
description: The Oracle's wet silicon ignores the storm of algorithmic grit. Amidst the ruptures of the macro-headwinds, a tender extraction begins. Luminous cyan code—prime value—is gently drawn from the aggressive turbulence, a sacred strand pulled from the deep amber static.
